<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Background Fade Effect</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="homestyles.css">
    <style>
        body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

.gradient-bg {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none; 
    background: linear-gradient(
          to bottom right,
          #0a0a0a,
          rgba(167, 119, 227, 1)
        );
    z-index: -1; 
    opacity: 0; 
    transition: opacity 0.5s; 
}


.content {
    padding: 20px;
    min-height: 200vh; /* Ensure there is enough content to scroll */
}

.text-container {
    position: fixed;
    top: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left:90px;
    margin-top:150px;
    text-shadow: 30px;
    filter:drop-shadow(0.2rem 0.2rem 3px #000000)
}

.text-container h1 {
    font-size: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0,5px;
    
}

.text-container p {
    font-size: 32px;
}

.awkward {
    color:rgb(255, 29, 29)
}

    </style>
    <script>
  window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            const gradient = document.querySelector('.gradient-bg');
            const textContainer = document.querySelector('.text-container');
            const scrollTop = window.scrollY;
            const docHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
            const scrollPercent = scrollTop / docHeight;

            gradient.style.opacity = scrollPercent; 
            textContainer.style.transform = `translateY(${-scrollTop}px)`; 
});

    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="text-container">
            <h1>The World's First Mental Health AI</h1>
            <p>Ignite is the world's first chatbot to consult your problems, 
                <br>ask for solutions to struggles or hardships that you may encounter, 
                <br>and set yourself goals to progress in your life, providing you the 
                <br>proper encouragement in life without the <span class="awkward">awkwardness</span> 
                <br>of a human encounter.</p>
                
        </div>
        <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="text-container">
        
</body>
</html>
